Sentencas: operation of cone-shaped anode-supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell (SIS-SOFC) stack directly on methane is studied.
Titulo: Direct operation of cone-shaped anode-supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell stack with methane

Sentencas: A cone-shaped solid oxide fuel cell stack is assembled by connecting 11 cone-shaped anode-supported single cells in series.
Titulo: Direct operation of cone-shaped anode-supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell stack with methane

Sentencas: The 11-cell-stack provides a maximum power output of about 8 W (421.4 mW cm(-2) calculated using active cathode area) at 800 degrees C and 6W (310.8 mW cm(-2)) at 700 degrees C, when operated with humidified methane fuel.
Titulo: Direct operation of cone-shaped anode-supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell stack with methane

Sentencas: The maximum volumetric power density of the stack is 0.9 W cm(-1) at 800 degrees C. Good stability is observed during 10 periods of thermal cycling test.
Titulo: Direct operation of cone-shaped anode-supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell stack with methane

Sentencas: SEM-EDX measurements are taken for analyzing the microstructures and the coking degrees.
Titulo: Direct operation of cone-shaped anode-supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell stack with methane
